Emilia.

584
00:28:10,000 --> 00:28:11,708
Is she...

585
00:28:13,875 --> 00:28:16,000
[door creaks]

586
00:28:17,125 --> 00:28:18,833
[crying]

587
00:28:22,166 --> 00:28:23,083
[music ends]

