[bell tolling]

604
00:29:15,208 --> 00:29:17,333
- Are you okay?

605
00:29:17,416 --> 00:29:19,333
[bell continues]

606
00:29:19,416 --> 00:29:20,833
[sighs]

607
00:29:22,416 --> 00:29:23,583
- Subaru.
- KADOMON: Hey!

608
00:29:23,666 --> 00:29:26,083
- What's wrong? Do you feel ill?

609
00:29:26,166 --> 00:29:28,458
- [gasps]

610
00:29:28,541 --> 00:29:29,250
- Um...

611
00:29:29,333 --> 00:29:31,041
what's the matter?

612
00:29:31,125 --> 00:29:31,875
[yelps]

613
00:29:31,958 --> 00:29:34,250
- Whoa! Wait, Subaru!
- Aw, come on now.

614
00:29:34,333 --> 00:29:35,500
- What's wrong? What is it?
- Easy, easy.

615
00:29:35,583 --> 00:29:36,916
Not in front of my shop.

616
00:29:37,000 --> 00:29:39,833
- Calm down, please.
- [sobbing]

617
00:29:39,916 --> 00:29:41,208
- Are you okay?

618
00:29:45,416 --> 00:29:47,500
[music playing]

619
00:29:49,125 --> 00:29:50,208
- I'm pretty sure

620
00:29:50,291 --> 00:29:53,166
there's neothing any of us
can do to help him.

621
00:29:53,250 --> 00:29:54,083
His wounds are one thing,

622
00:29:54,166 --> 00:29:56,500
but there's neo helping
his mental state.

623
00:29:56,583 --> 00:29:59,250
- Do you know how this happened?

624
00:29:59,333 --> 00:30:02,333
- No clue. I've checked
every inch of him, but...

625
00:30:02,416 --> 00:30:04,958
- What are the odds
of it being a curse?

626
00:30:05,041 --> 00:30:06,875
- Pretty low.
There's neo indication

627
00:30:06,958 --> 00:30:09,333
of any interference using mana.

628
00:30:09,416 --> 00:30:11,125
[Crusch sighs]

629
00:30:11,208 --> 00:30:14,208
If Felix is unable to help,
I'm afraid that no one

630
00:30:14,291 --> 00:30:16,916
in this household
can do anything to heal him.

631
00:30:17,000 --> 00:30:18,291
Sorry we can't assist you.

632
00:30:18,375 --> 00:30:20,541
- No, I can't thank you enough
for everything you've done,

633
00:30:20,625 --> 00:30:23,333
as well
as your generous concern.

634
00:30:25,083 --> 00:30:26,125
<i>He's right.</i>

635
00:30:26,208 --> 00:30:28,791
<i>There's no mana interference,</i>
<i>but...</i>

636
00:30:31,500 --> 00:30:32,916
<i>the Witch's miasma.</i>

637
00:30:35,291 --> 00:30:38,083
Thank you for everything.

638
00:30:38,166 --> 00:30:39,625
I thank you in my master's stead

639
00:30:39,708 --> 00:30:42,166
for your kindness and
hospitality during our stay.

640
00:30:42,250 --> 00:30:45,166
- Please give Emilia
this message as well.

641
00:30:45,250 --> 00:30:46,583
Let us compete for the throne

642
00:30:46,666 --> 00:30:49,083
in a manner that will bring
neither of us shame.

643
00:30:49,583 --> 00:30:51,416
- FELIX: Hey.
- Hmm?

644
00:30:51,500 --> 00:30:53,416
- I understand why you're
going back to the mansion,

645
00:30:53,500 --> 00:30:56,250
but can anyone there heal him?

646
00:30:56,333 --> 00:30:59,875
- He utters our names,
albeit only occasionally.

647
00:30:59,958 --> 00:31:02,250
He says my name,
my sister's name, also...

648
00:31:02,333 --> 00:31:04,875
Miss Emilia's.

649
00:31:04,958 --> 00:31:06,541
I'm hoping
that if he can see her,

650
00:31:06,625 --> 00:31:09,041
maybe his condition will change.

651
00:31:11,541 --> 00:31:14,000
- I realize this is tasteless,
but I must ask you something.

652
00:31:15,958 --> 00:31:18,041
How can you give
so much of yourself

653
00:31:18,125 --> 00:31:18,916
for Subaru Natsuki?

654
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:21,875
Your relationship with him
is not the same

655
00:31:21,958 --> 00:31:25,125
as that of a master and servant,
like Felix and mine,

656
00:31:25,208 --> 00:31:27,541
but I hesitate to conclude
that your behavior

657
00:31:27,625 --> 00:31:30,375
and the glances you cast
are those a woman gives a man.

658
00:31:33,250 --> 00:31:35,416
I'm sorry.
That's really too forward.

659
00:31:35,500 --> 00:31:37,291
- Forget I said--
- No. No, it's not that.

660
00:31:37,375 --> 00:31:38,458
It's just...

661
00:31:38,541 --> 00:31:41,125
well, how can I put it?

662
00:31:42,375 --> 00:31:43,291
You see...

663
00:31:47,625 --> 00:31:52,125
