is really special to me.

664
00:31:52,208 --> 00:31:53,208
- [gasps]
- Huh?

665
00:31:54,333 --> 00:31:55,500
- Um...

666
00:31:55,583 --> 00:31:57,625
CRUSCH: Please, forgive me.

