00:31:57,708 --> 00:32:00,041
I was stunned speechless
for a moment.

668
00:32:01,250 --> 00:32:03,583
I'd say Subaru Natsuki
is a lucky man.

669
00:32:03,666 --> 00:32:06,166
- Hah! You can say that again.
If he ever recovers,

670
00:32:06,250 --> 00:32:08,250
