to tease him to the max.

671
00:32:08,333 --> 00:32:09,458
- [giggles]

672
00:32:09,541 --> 00:32:11,166
- Safe travels.

673
00:32:11,250 --> 00:32:12,458
- Good luck with everything.

674
00:32:12,541 --> 00:32:14,500
[music playing]

675
00:32:32,500 --> 00:32:34,083
[fire crackling]

676
00:32:34,166 --> 00:32:38,000
- I know I mustn't let
my personal feelings interfere,

677
00:32:38,083 --> 00:32:40,041
but...

678
00:32:40,125 --> 00:32:42,625
if I'm being completely honest
with myself,

679
00:32:42,708 --> 00:32:44,125
I felt happy to have

680
00:32:44,208 --> 00:32:47,208
so much one-on-one time with you
at Miss Crusch's house.

681
00:32:47,291 --> 00:32:48,541
I realize once we
get back to the mansion,

682
00:32:48,625 --> 00:32:51,083
