683
00:32:52,458 --> 00:32:54,583
Even though I knew
something was troubling you,

684
00:32:54,666 --> 00:32:56,083
I'm sorry.

685
00:32:56,166 --> 00:32:59,541
Even though I heard that you
had quarreled with Miss
Emilia,

686
00:32:59,625 --> 00:33:01,416
causing a rift
between the two of you,

687
00:33:01,500 --> 00:33:03,125
- I'm sorry.
- [ground dragon sighs]

688
00:33:03,208 --> 00:33:04,416
- I know you'll be all right.

689
00:33:04,500 --> 00:33:07,208
Just you wait.

690
00:33:07,291 --> 00:33:08,958
You're demonically inspired.

691
00:33:14,833 --> 00:33:15,458
And so driven.

692
00:33:15,541 --> 00:33:18,166
You're a remarkable person.

693
00:33:23,750 --> 00:33:25,750
[carriage rattling]

694
00:33:34,416 --> 00:33:36,458
<i>It's too quiet.</i>

695
00:33:36,541 --> 00:33:37,583
[gasps]

696
00:33:37,666 --> 00:33:40,166
[panting]

697
00:33:40,250 --> 00:33:42,500
<i>That was Sister! She's...</i>

698
00:33:42,583 --> 00:33:44,291
<i>I have to get back quickly.</i>

699
00:33:49,458 --> 00:33:51,416
[wind blowing]

700
00:33:53,375 --> 00:33:56,041
- [groans]

701
00:33:58,291 --> 00:34:00,625
