00:34:29,708 --> 00:34:31,458
<i>Huma!</i>

710
00:34:32,541 --> 00:34:33,458
[winces]

711
00:34:33,541 --> 00:34:35,708
[gasps] Subaru!

712
00:34:39,291 --> 00:34:40,208
Bring him back! [gasps]

713
00:34:43,416 --> 00:34:46,333
You bastards.

714
00:34:46,416 --> 00:34:48,666
You stole my sister's horn

715
00:34:48,750 --> 00:34:52,291
