716
00:34:52,375 --> 00:34:53,666
But that wasn't enough?

717
00:34:53,750 --> 00:34:57,291
Now you've come here to steal
my reason to die, too!

718
00:34:57,375 --> 00:35:00,208
I'll kill you!

719
00:35:04,916 --> 00:35:07,541
[rumbling]

720
00:35:12,750 --> 00:35:14,500
[water dripping]

721
00:35:14,583 --> 00:35:16,541
- [hissing]

722
00:35:19,333 --> 00:35:19,625
- [gasps]

723
00:35:19,708 --> 00:35:22,833
- Yes, I see.

724
00:35:22,916 --> 00:35:26,291
This is certainly
an interesting development.

725
00:35:26,375 --> 00:35:27,541
So tell me...

726
00:35:27,625 --> 00:35:30,208
