00:35:31,833 --> 00:35:34,541
[knuckle creaking]

730
00:35:34,625 --> 00:35:37,500
[muffled] I guess you're
not going to answer me, are you?

731
00:35:37,583 --> 00:35:40,125
[gasps]

732
00:35:42,416 --> 00:35:44,416
Ah, right.

733
00:35:44,500 --> 00:35:46,250
