trivialities when I'm excited.

735
00:35:53,416 --> 00:35:55,916
I am a Sin Archbishop
of the Witch's Cult,

736
00:35:56,000 --> 00:35:58,458
representing Sloth,

737
00:35:58,541 --> 00:36:02,708
Betelgeuse Romanée-Conti, yes.

738
00:36:02,791 --> 00:36:04,500
[men's chorus vocalizing]

739
00:36:04,583 --> 00:36:06,833
- [stammering]

740
00:36:06,916 --> 00:36:10,583
- Ah, how utterly comical.

741
00:36:10,666 --> 00:36:11,833
What a very entertaining sight.

742
00:36:11,916 --> 00:36:15,458
[squeals] Very, very, very...

743
00:36:15,541 --> 00:36:18,708
truly, truly,
