744
00:36:18,791 --> 00:36:21,666
My brain trembles.

745
00:36:22,333 --> 00:36:24,916
Now, what has brought him here?

746
00:36:25,000 --> 00:36:25,583
- Dragon...
- Eh?

747
00:36:25,666 --> 00:36:27,625
- carriage.

748
00:36:27,708 --> 00:36:29,583
- Really?!

749
00:36:29,666 --> 00:36:30,916
Ah, aren't ground dragons great?

750
00:36:31,000 --> 00:36:33,916
