as a species diligently.

752
00:36:35,916 --> 00:36:38,333
They're just fantastic!

753
00:36:38,416 --> 00:36:39,958
- Killed.

754
00:36:40,041 --> 00:36:40,958
- [grunts]

755
00:36:41,041 --> 00:36:42,416
Of course.

756
00:36:42,500 --> 00:36:44,166
Your diligence
is following my orders

757
00:36:44,250 --> 00:36:46,750
