diligence itself, to the ground.

758
00:36:46,833 --> 00:36:49,500
Oh, my brain trembles,

759
00:36:49,583 --> 00:36:53,375
trembles, trembles, trembles!

760
00:36:54,708 --> 00:36:56,833
[hisses] Then again,
a dead ground dragon

761
00:36:56,916 --> 00:36:58,875
is the very definition
of sloth.

762
00:37:00,750 --> 00:37:02,583
Nonetheless,
we must push forward,

763
00:37:02,666 --> 00:37:03,291
clean up the area at once.

764
00:37:03,375 --> 00:37:05,500
With the day of the Ordeal
upon us,

765
00:37:05,583 --> 00:37:07,541
