to be discovered.

766
00:37:07,625 --> 00:37:09,583
What of his friend?

767
00:37:09,666 --> 00:37:11,500
- Unknown.
- Ah.

768
00:37:11,583 --> 00:37:13,958
Well, that presents
another dilemma.

769
00:37:14,041 --> 00:37:16,541
Unknown if she's alive or dead.

770
00:37:16,625 --> 00:37:18,833
That makes you...

771
00:37:18,916 --> 00:37:21,541
the truly slothful one.

772
00:37:22,000 --> 00:37:24,208
[shrieks] You fool!

773
00:37:24,291 --> 00:37:26,458
With the Ordeal before us,
you let a problem remain?

774
00:37:26,541 --> 00:37:28,875
Is this the sincerity you show
in return for our Gospel?!

775
00:37:28,958 --> 00:37:32,166
