776
00:37:32,250 --> 00:37:35,500
It's sloth! It's sloth!
It's sloth! It's sloth!

777
00:37:35,583 --> 00:37:37,375
Please forgive us the sloth

778
00:37:37,458 --> 00:37:40,458
that has led us
to betray your goodwill.

779
00:37:40,541 --> 00:37:41,375
Ah, yes, love.

780
00:37:41,458 --> 00:37:44,000
We must repay love
with love, with love.

781
00:37:44,083 --> 00:37:45,833
Bring the girl here.

782
00:37:45,916 --> 00:37:47,125
If she lives, then kill her.

783
00:37:47,208 --> 00:37:50,875
If she doesn't,
then bring me her bloody head!

784
00:37:50,958 --> 00:37:52,416
It's love!

785
00:37:52,500 --> 00:37:55,541
We must repay love with love!

786
00:37:55,625 --> 00:37:57,333
[chorus vocalizing]

787
00:38:02,583 --> 00:38:03,791
Now then.

788
00:38:03,875 --> 00:38:05,041
Now then. Now then.

789
00:38:05,125 --> 00:38:07,458
Now then. Now then.
Now then. Now then.

790
00:38:09,666 --> 00:38:11,291
- [moans]
- Now then...

791
00:38:11,375 --> 00:38:13,583
you will look deep into my eyes.

792
00:38:14,958 --> 00:38:15,750
Answer me,

793
00:38:15,833 --> 00:38:18,958
and be sure to choose
your words carefully.

794
00:38:19,041 --> 00:38:21,791
I want you to tell me
why such dense pangs of love

795
00:38:21,875 --> 00:38:24,166
hang with sheer abundance
upon your person.

796
00:38:24,250 --> 00:38:27,875
Do you not own
a copy of the Gospel?

797
00:38:29,625 --> 00:38:31,416
- Huh?

798
00:38:31,500 --> 00:38:34,458
- Oh, it saddens me
to be ignored!

799
00:38:34,541 --> 00:38:36,208
I treated you so kindly,
and yet and yet

800
00:38:36,291 --> 00:38:38,791
and yet and yet and yet
and yet and yet and yet and--

801
00:38:38,875 --> 00:38:40,375
[babbles]

802
00:38:40,458 --> 00:38:43,083
In that case, I will change
the order of my questions.

803
00:38:44,458 --> 00:38:44,916
Let me ask you this...

804
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:47,625
- [slurps]
- [wincing]

805
00:38:49,041 --> 00:38:49,791
[joints popping]

806
00:38:49,875 --> 00:38:52,541
...as I'm curious.

807
00:38:52,625 --> 00:38:55,666
Why do you pretend
that your mind is broken?

808
00:38:55,750 --> 00:38:56,958
[chorus continues]

809
00:38:58,000 --> 00:38:58,958
- [sighs]

810
00:39:00,291 --> 00:39:01,125
[sighs]

811
00:39:01,208 --> 00:39:03,750
- No, no, no, no.

812
00:39:03,833 --> 00:39:06,458
I truly have my doubts about
your state of mind right now,

813
00:39:06,541 --> 00:39:08,583
which is why I ask why,
for what reason,

814
00:39:08,666 --> 00:39:09,916
for what purpose,
for what resolution,

815
00:39:10,000 --> 00:39:12,625
for what possible outcome
do you act so utterly crazed?

816
00:39:12,708 --> 00:39:13,958
- [shudders]

817
00:39:14,041 --> 00:39:16,041
- Your so-called insanity
is far too sane.

818
00:39:16,125 --> 00:39:19,000
To behave so cleverly
and quietly

819
00:39:19,083 --> 00:39:21,041
as if seeking sympathy
for your situation,

820
00:39:21,125 --> 00:39:23,916
it is a demeaning insult,
a true madness.

821
00:39:24,000 --> 00:39:27,000
- [groaning]

822
00:39:27,083 --> 00:39:30,083
- You are a fake,
a poorly acted madman.

823
00:39:30,166 --> 00:39:31,916
If your insanity was genuine,

824
00:39:32,000 --> 00:39:34,833
you would pay no heed
to the gazes of others.

825
00:39:34,916 --> 00:39:36,833
- [sobbing]

826
00:39:36,916 --> 00:39:38,000
- [laughs] How comical.

827
00:39:38,083 --> 00:39:40,833
How completely comical!

828
00:39:40,916 --> 00:39:42,791
- [laughs]
- [weeps]

829
00:39:42,875 --> 00:39:45,708
- How I pity you.

830
00:39:45,791 --> 00:39:48,416
I pity
your wretched, despicable,

831
00:39:48,500 --> 00:39:50,000
wicked, ugly, lowly,
diminutive, sinful being

832
00:39:50,083 --> 00:39:52,875
from the bottom of my heart.

833
00:39:52,958 --> 00:39:54,625
Yet despite those shortcomings,

834
00:39:54,708 --> 00:39:56,791
you are so loved!

835
00:39:56,875 --> 00:39:59,208
[yelps] You mean
that you'd rather waste away

836
00:39:59,291 --> 00:40:02,416
in stagnation than repay
the goodwill shown to you?

837
00:40:07,875 --> 00:40:09,958
That makes you...

838
00:40:10,041 --> 00:40:12,666
truly slothful.

839
00:40:12,750 --> 00:40:14,916
- [rocks falling]
- Oh?

840
00:40:20,833 --> 00:40:22,250
[chain jangling]

841
00:40:22,333 --> 00:40:24,000
[music playing]

842
00:40:24,083 --> 00:40:25,708
- I found your lair.

843
00:40:27,750 --> 00:40:28,833
What have you done?!

844
00:40:28,916 --> 00:40:30,125
- [wails]

845
00:40:30,208 --> 00:40:33,708
How absolutely fantastic
this is!

846
00:40:33,791 --> 00:40:36,125
A girl, a lone girl,
is so badly injured.

847
00:40:36,208 --> 00:40:38,500
Yet she presses on for this boy!

848
00:40:38,583 --> 00:40:41,375
- That's enough
of your nonsense, Witch Cultist!

849
00:40:41,458 --> 00:40:43,291
You're fools to carry out
your insubordinate acts

850
00:40:43,375 --> 00:40:47,500
in Lord Roswaal's domain
without his permission!

851
00:40:47,583 --> 00:40:49,500
In my absent master's stead,

852
00:40:49,583 --> 00:40:51,875
I will bring
the death penalty upon you!

853
00:40:51,958 --> 00:40:54,000
- And you'll do all that
in your battered state?

854
00:40:54,083 --> 00:40:56,166
Correct me if I'm wrong,

855
00:40:56,250 --> 00:40:58,375
but you really only came here
to retrieve this boy,

856
00:40:58,458 --> 00:41:00,291
and if that's the case,
you should stop saying

857
00:41:00,375 --> 00:41:02,041
these tempting things
that sound, oh, so attractive.

858
00:41:02,125 --> 00:41:04,250
- Don't you touch him.

859
00:41:04,333 --> 00:41:06,708
- Eh? What was that?

860
00:41:06,791 --> 00:41:08,625
- I said don't you touch him!

861
00:41:10,666 --> 00:41:11,833
- [squeals]

862
00:41:11,916 --> 00:41:14,375
That shot was utterly fantastic,
a work of art,

863
00:41:14,458 --> 00:41:16,125
but tell me, why does such
a believer in love as yourself

864
00:41:16,208 --> 00:41:18,958
adhere to someone like him?

865
00:41:19,041 --> 00:41:21,250
- You know nothing
about Subaru, bastard!

866
00:41:21,333 --> 00:41:22,625
<i>El Huma!</i>

867
00:41:24,208 --> 00:41:26,000
- Oh. Oh. Amazing.

868
00:41:26,083 --> 00:41:27,708
That was nothing short
of amazing.

869
00:41:27,791 --> 00:41:28,875
- [groans]

870
00:41:28,958 --> 00:41:32,000
[chorus vocalizing]

871
00:41:32,083 --> 00:41:33,000
- [moans]

872
00:41:36,625 --> 00:41:36,958
Rem.

873
00:41:37,041 --> 00:41:39,208
[chorus continues]

874
00:41:41,166 --> 00:41:43,041
[no audible dialogue]

875
00:41:43,125 --> 00:41:44,250
[chorus ends]

876
00:41:44,333 --> 00:41:46,625
- My brain trembles.

877
00:41:47,250 --> 00:41:49,791
- [bones cracking]
- [grunts]

878
00:41:49,875 --> 00:41:50,833
[silence]

879
00:41:53,083 --> 00:41:55,750
[robe flutters]

880
00:41:55,833 --> 00:41:57,041
- By the Authority of Sloth,

881
00:41:57,125 --> 00:42:00,333
I summon the Unseen Hand.

882
00:42:02,833 --> 00:42:03,916
Look at her, boy.

883
00:42:04,000 --> 00:42:05,000
- Just look at her.
- [moans]

884
00:42:05,083 --> 00:42:07,791
- This is a result
of your actions.

885
00:42:07,875 --> 00:42:10,166
- By doing nothing,
you practiced sloth,

886
00:42:10,250 --> 00:42:12,791
and because of that,
the girl is dead.

887
00:42:12,875 --> 00:42:15,041
You killed her.
It was all your doing!

888
00:42:15,125 --> 00:42:17,666
Or more to the point,
your lack of doing anything!

889
00:42:17,750 --> 00:42:19,250
How awful! How completely awful!

890
00:42:19,333 --> 00:42:21,708
- SUBARU: You...
- With my arm,

891
00:42:21,791 --> 00:42:22,250
with my fingers, it was you.

892
00:42:22,333 --> 00:42:24,708
It was you. It was you.

893
00:42:24,791 --> 00:42:27,750
[shrill]
It was you! It was you!

894
00:42:28,875 --> 00:42:31,333
You killed her.

895
00:42:31,875 --> 00:42:33,791
- Stop it.

896
00:42:33,875 --> 00:42:34,291
- "It hurts.

897
00:42:34,375 --> 00:42:36,625
"It hurts! It hurts!

898
00:42:36,708 --> 00:42:39,666
"Help me. Help me!

899
00:42:39,750 --> 00:42:40,875
"Agh! Help me!

900
00:42:40,958 --> 00:42:41,833
Help me!"

901
00:42:41,916 --> 00:42:47,208
[shrieks]

902
00:42:47,291 --> 00:42:49,125
[hisses] "Subaru, please help."

903
00:42:50,416 --> 00:42:54,041
- Betelgeuse!

904
00:42:54,125 --> 00:42:56,541
I'll kill you!

905
00:42:56,625 --> 00:42:58,333
- I'll kill you! I'll kill you!
- [laughing]

906
00:42:58,416 --> 00:43:01,583
I finally got you
to call me by my name.

907
00:43:01,666 --> 00:43:03,083
I'm deeply touched
by your kind gesture.

908
00:43:03,166 --> 00:43:05,000
- I'll kill you!

909
00:43:05,083 --> 00:43:08,000
I'll kill you,
you son of a bitch! Die!

910
00:43:08,083 --> 00:43:09,916
- Die, damn it!
- [murmurs]

911
00:43:10,000 --> 00:43:11,666
- [wailing]
- [giggles]

912
00:43:11,750 --> 00:43:13,166
This place has turned
into quite the mess, hasn't it?

913
00:43:13,250 --> 00:43:15,833
I'll just leave it!

914
00:43:15,916 --> 00:43:17,250
All right, men.

915
00:43:17,333 --> 00:43:19,833
Time for you to resume
your previously planned duties

916
00:43:19,916 --> 00:43:21,958
and rendezvous
with the other fingers.

917
00:43:22,041 --> 00:43:24,958
The Ordeal will proceed
on the scheduled day.

918
00:43:25,041 --> 00:43:26,833
- [Subaru wailing]
- Now, as for you and

919
00:43:26,916 --> 00:43:29,208
- your position in all this...
- Bastard, I'll kill you...

920
00:43:29,291 --> 00:43:30,000
- to be completely honest
with you,

921
00:43:30,083 --> 00:43:32,541
I have no idea what it is,

922
00:43:32,625 --> 00:43:35,333
so I shall simply judge you
as our lord sees fit.

923
00:43:35,416 --> 00:43:36,666
- [screaming]

924
00:43:36,750 --> 00:43:38,000
- I will leave you bound here.

925
00:43:38,083 --> 00:43:40,791
Should the Gospel happen
to find its way to you,

926
00:43:40,875 --> 00:43:43,291
I'm sure you'll be saved
in divine intervention.

927
00:43:43,375 --> 00:43:45,208
- Kill you!

928
00:43:45,291 --> 00:43:47,208
- [laughing]
- I'll kill--

929
00:43:47,291 --> 00:43:49,708
I will kill you, you bastard!

930
00:43:49,791 --> 00:43:51,750
- [laughing]
- You hear me?!

931
00:43:51,833 --> 00:43:54,000
- I'll kill you. I'll kill you!
- Oh?

932
00:43:54,083 --> 00:43:57,208
Ah, yes, you were also
a believer in love.

933
00:43:57,291 --> 00:43:59,708
You sacrificed yourself for it,
defying your own faith,

934
00:43:59,791 --> 00:44:02,875
but you fell just before
your feelings reached him,

935
00:44:02,958 --> 00:44:04,875
leaving your love
with nowhere to go,

936
00:44:04,958 --> 00:44:07,083
unknown, unheard,
and unrequited.

937
00:44:07,166 --> 00:44:09,250
- I'll kill you!
- [chuckles]

938
00:44:09,333 --> 00:44:12,875
That makes you
a truly slothful one.

939
00:44:12,958 --> 00:44:15,125
- I'll kill you. I'll kill you.
- [laughing]

940
00:44:15,208 --> 00:44:16,875
I'll kill you. I'll kill you!

941
00:44:16,958 --> 00:44:18,166
I'll kill you.

942
00:44:18,250 --> 00:44:20,250
- [laughing]
- [screaming]

943
00:44:25,000 --> 00:44:25,958
[scream fades]

944
00:44:29,916 --> 00:44:30,583
[weakly] I'll kill you.

945
00:44:30,666 --> 00:44:32,875
- I'll kill you.
- [head thumps]

946
00:44:32,958 --> 00:44:35,000
I'll kill you. I'll kill you.

947
00:44:35,083 --> 00:44:36,916
[gasps] I'll kill you.

948
00:44:37,000 --> 00:44:39,166
I'll kill you.

949
00:44:39,250 --> 00:44:40,916
I'll kill you.

950
00:44:44,958 --> 00:44:46,166
[groans]

951
00:44:46,250 --> 00:44:48,208
[shuffling]

952
00:44:53,875 --> 00:44:55,833
Eh? Rem?

953
00:44:57,000 --> 00:44:59,000
[scrapes]

954
00:45:00,041 --> 00:45:01,208
You're alive?

955
00:45:01,291 --> 00:45:03,250
[music playing]

956
00:45:07,291 --> 00:45:08,416
Rem-Rem.

957
00:45:08,500 --> 00:45:11,041
Rem-Rem. Thank God.

958
00:45:11,125 --> 00:45:12,291
Rem!

959
00:45:12,375 --> 00:45:14,083
I was so worried!

960
00:45:14,166 --> 00:45:16,958
Rem! [groans]

961
00:45:17,041 --> 00:45:18,958
[groaning]

962
00:45:24,208 --> 00:45:25,458
You okay?

963
00:45:25,541 --> 00:45:27,375
Hey, Rem.

964
00:45:27,458 --> 00:45:29,375
-<i> Hu...</i>
- [gasps]

965
00:45:29,458 --> 00:45:30,583
-<i> ...ma.</i>

966
00:45:31,875 --> 00:45:33,166
[metal shatters]

967
00:45:33,250 --> 00:45:35,375
- Rem, wh-what'd you do?

968
00:45:36,041 --> 00:45:37,000
- Please...

969
00:45:37,083 --> 00:45:38,916
stay...

970
00:45:39,000 --> 00:45:39,958
alive.

971
00:45:40,041 --> 00:45:41,791
- Rem, wait.

972
00:45:41,875 --> 00:45:43,791
No. Don't leave me.

973
00:45:50,208 --> 00:45:51,291
- Live...

974
00:45:51,375 --> 00:45:52,541
for...

975
00:45:52,625 --> 00:45:53,583
me.

976
00:45:54,125 --> 00:45:56,208
I...

977
00:45:56,291 --> 00:45:58,125
love you.

978
00:46:02,000 --> 00:46:02,916
- Rem?

979
00:46:05,166 --> 00:46:07,791
[crying]

980
00:46:13,291 --> 00:46:15,000
[crying fades]

981
00:46:15,083 --> 00:46:17,083
[music playing]

982
00:46:25,041 --> 00:46:25,916
Okay, Rem. Let's go.

983
00:46:32,083 --> 00:46:33,291
[music continues]

984
00:46:37,041 --> 00:46:39,000
[gasping]

985
00:46:53,125 --> 00:46:55,041
[snow crunching]

986
00:46:55,125 --> 00:46:57,041
Damn you, Betelgeuse.

987
00:47:00,666 --> 00:47:02,500
Damn you, Betelgeuse.

988
00:47:05,541 --> 00:47:07,875
[wind gusting]

989
00:47:22,041 --> 00:47:24,291
[crying]

990
00:47:24,375 --> 00:47:26,041
Betelgeuse, damn you!

991
00:47:26,125 --> 00:47:28,666
[crying]

992
00:47:30,250 --> 00:47:33,250
Betelgeuse!

993
00:47:33,333 --> 00:47:36,083
[rumbling]

994
00:47:41,625 --> 00:47:43,250
PUCK: Sleep...

995
00:47:43,333 --> 00:47:45,208
along with my daughter.

996
00:47:50,166 --> 00:47:51,916
[instrumental playing]

997
00:49:22,666 --> 00:49:24,208
KADOMON: Hey.

998
00:49:24,291 --> 00:49:25,583
- [gasps]
- You listening?

999
00:49:25,666 --> 00:49:28,250
- Huh?
- Now, don't you "huh" me.

1000
00:49:28,333 --> 00:49:29,208
What's your problem?

1001
00:49:29,291 --> 00:49:30,166
It's like
you suddenly spaced out.

1002
00:49:30,250 --> 00:49:31,333
- I, uh...

1003
00:49:31,416 --> 00:49:33,208
REM: Subaru.

1004
00:49:34,791 --> 00:49:35,708
- Rem-Rem.

1005
00:49:35,791 --> 00:49:37,416
- Yes?

1006
00:49:37,500 --> 00:49:39,416
What's the matter?

1007
00:49:39,500 --> 00:49:42,125
You look like
you've just seen a ghost.

1008
00:49:43,375 --> 00:49:44,791
- It's you.
- Me?

1009
00:49:44,875 --> 00:49:46,541
What is it?

1010
00:49:46,625 --> 00:49:47,708
- Rem-Rem.

1011
00:49:47,791 --> 00:49:48,750
- Yes?

1012
00:49:50,291 --> 00:49:51,333
- I'm just...
- Look...

1013
00:49:51,416 --> 00:49:54,583
I hate to interrupt when you're
just getting heated up,

1014
00:49:54,666 --> 00:49:57,333
but I can't do business
with you two flirtin' there.

1015
00:49:57,416 --> 00:49:59,333
[market chatter]

1016
00:49:59,416 --> 00:50:01,208
REM: Do you think
I could ask you something?

1017
00:50:01,291 --> 00:50:02,541
- What is it?

1018
00:50:02,625 --> 00:50:04,541
- Well, I may be mistaken,

1019
00:50:04,625 --> 00:50:06,416
but it's just, um...

1020
00:50:06,500 --> 00:50:09,583
that unpleasant odor.

1021
00:50:09,666 --> 00:50:12,458
It seems to have grown
even stronger on you.

1022
00:50:14,250 --> 00:50:16,083
- Unpleasant odor, huh.

1023
00:50:16,166 --> 00:50:17,750
Well, if that's got you worried,

1024
00:50:17,833 --> 00:50:19,500
then you can
just keep holding my hand.

1025
00:50:19,583 --> 00:50:20,875
- Huh?

1026
00:50:20,958 --> 00:50:23,250
I mean, it feels a lot safer
like this, doesn't it?

1027
00:50:23,333 --> 00:50:24,708
- [gasps]

1028
00:50:24,791 --> 00:50:25,708
Yes.

